    - Baic debain 12 installation with basic toosl
    - 🖥️ Xorg display system
    - 📊 polybar (panel)
    - 🔍 rofi (launcher)
    - 🔔 dunst (notifications)
    - 📡 network-manager (tray applet)
    - 🔊 pipewire + pavucontrol (audio)
    - 📂 thunar (file manager)
    - 💻 kitty (terminal)
    - ⚙️ x11 utilities (xrandr, xsetroot, xrdb, etc.)
0. Before Installation

sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y \
xserver-xorg \
xinit \
x11-xserver-utils \
x11-utils \
mesa-utils \
bspwm \
sxhkd \
polybar \
rofi \
picom \
nitrogen \
dunst \
network-manager-gnome \
blueman \
pipewire \
pipewire-audio \
pavucontrol \
thunar \
kitty \
lxappearance \
xfce4-power-manager \
fonts-dejavu \
fonts-noto



1. Window Manager
    - 🪟 bspwm + sxhkd (tiling WM + keybindings)
2. Display Manager
    - Ly or SDDM (maybe CDM but it looks too... idk)
3. Compository
    - 🌌 picom (compositor)
4. Additional Utilities
    4.1 Wallpaper Setter
        - 🖼 feh (wallpaper)
        - 🖼 nitrogen 
    4.2 Bar
        - Preferebly Polybar
    4.3 Application launcher
        - Rofi
    4.4 System Tray
        - Polybar's Internal Tray module
    4.5 Polkit
        - Polkit-1 ?? (maybe xfce-polkit)

